These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
House: colonial, cape-cod, futuristic, ranch-style, cottage
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
City: boston, liverpool, hannover, london, nizza
 1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person traveling to nizza is the cottage house##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the cape-cod house##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the colonial house is on the right of the british##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person traveling to boston##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| House         | cape-cod  | colonial    | ranch-style | futuristic    | cottage  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| City         | hannover | london    | liverpool | boston  | nizza |

