.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, poker, domino, whist
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, architect, dressmaker, photographer, scientist
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, ship, car, motorbike, helicopter
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the photographer is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is the person driving the ship##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person playing poker is the person driving the car##1
 9. the russian is the person playing poker##1
10. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
11. the person playing domino is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the person playing poker is the architect##1
13. the person playing whist is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Game          | poker        | whist | scrabble     | domino      | billiard  |
| Job           | architect   | dressmaker | scientist    | photographer | accountant |
| Transport   | car | motorbike     | helicopter | trike    | ship  |
| Nationality   | russian     | indonesian | argentine    | spanish      | mexican    |

