.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
House: colonial, tower, futuristic, victorian, cape-cod
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, traveling, writing
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, february, june, september, july
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile, train
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
 4. the tower house is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the cape-cod house is on the right of the colonial house##1
13. the victorian house is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| House      | victorian          | futuristic  | tower       | colonial     | cape-cod      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | traveling  | reading   | cooking    |
| Birthday   | february        | july | october | september    | june   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | scooter | train      | quad-bike | snowmobile |

