 4. the person who growsdahlia is the dressmaker##1
 5. the paramedic is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the nurse##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating zucchini is the person who growsdaisy##1
11. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
