The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, sailing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the mechanic##1
 3. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 6. the designer is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the photographer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
 9. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
