The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, ice-hockey, lacrosse, weightlifting
 1. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 3. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person eating cabbage##1
 9. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating peach##1
11. the person who likes pink is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Color         | white  | black  | pink    | lilac | aquamarine |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy        | fantasy  | scientific | epic      | sports        |
