 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
11. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
