The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, electronic, folk, r&b, soul
The people have 5 different jobs:  writer, teacher, project-manager, freelancer, dressmaker
 1. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the dressmaker is on the right of the fan of country##1
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is the writer##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the writer is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person drinking water is the fan of electronic##1
 8. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
10. the project-manager is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is the fan of folk##1
12. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
13. the teacher is on the left of the project-manager##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |      4       |     5      |
