 4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is the owner of the rat##1
12. the owner of the cat is the person traveling to marseilles##1
13. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
