.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, malaysian, spanish, nigerian, french
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, van, skateboard, airplane, tram
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, house, reggae
5 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, mouse, pony, rabbit
 1. the person driving the van is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the russian is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the fan of country##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person driving the van is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the nigerian##1
10. the french is on the right of the malaysian##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
12. the person driving the skateboard is the fan of house##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Nationality      | russian      | malaysian       | french         | nigerian  | spanish |
| Transport   | skateboard  | airplane | van | taxi  | tram  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | country    | blues        | reggae | folk     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

