.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily, amaryllis, balloon-flower, rose
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, gospel, jazz
5 different games are played: poker, monopoly, mah-jongg, snooker, bridge
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, sailing, swimming, volleyball
 1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person who growslily is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan of country##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
10. the person playing poker is the fan of jazz##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Flower   | lily      | balloon-flower | amaryllis  | rose    | azalea |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | jazz     | country | blues      | folk      |
| Game           | mah-jongg       | poker     | monopoly     | bridge     | snooker   |
| Sport         | basketball | swimming | rowing  | volleyball | sailing   |

