.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, sprite
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, orange, amber, emerald, red
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, may, february, july, december
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes emerald is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person who likes amber is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes red is in the middle##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | milk    | cola       | sprite |
| Color   | amber           | orange   | red   | emerald       | light-blue  |
| Birthday   | may       | january | february | july     | december   |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | scooter   | train   | helicopter | tram   |

 